        {
          "step": 1,
          "title": "Rectangle probability",
          "content": "∫₀^{1/2}∫_{1/4}^{1/2} 4xy dy dx = ∫₀^{1/2} 2x[y²/2]_{1/4}^{1/2} dx ≈ 0.0469",
          "explanation": "Integrate inner then outer."
        },
        {
          "step": 2,
          "title": "P(X<Y)",
          "content": "∫₀¹∫_x¹ 4xy dy dx = ∫₀¹ 2x(1-x²) dx = 1/2",
          "explanation": "Region above diagonal in unit square."
        }
      ],
      "finalAnswer": "P(rectangle)≈0.047, P(X<Y)=0.5",
